<h1>Send Feedbin Pages to Kindle</h1>

<p>This service takes the articles saved to your <a href="https://feedbin.com">Feedbin Pages</a> account and wraps them into a bespoke, artisanally crafted ebook (mobi). We send the ebook to your Feedbin email address, and you can send it to your Kindle.</p>
<p>Privacy Policy: We don't store your Feedbin credentials at all. We fetch your content, build a book and send it to you, and then we no longer have your passwords.</p>

<form action="/" method="POST">
  <% if (errors.length) { %>
    <div class="errors">
      <h3>Errors:</h3>
      <ul>
        <% errors.forEach(error => { %>
          <li><%= error %></li>
        <% }); %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  <% } %>
  <p><label>Your Feedbin Username: <input type="text" name="username" value="" placeholder="myfeedbinaccount@gmail.com" /></label></p>
  <p><label>Your Feedbin Password: <input type="password" name="password" value="" placeholder="Shhh... secret..." /></label></p>
  <button type="submit">Let's do it!</button>
</form>

